v><div class='interlinear-verse'><p><span class='greek-word'>ἐπιτελοῦντες</span><span class='greek-word'>ἁγιωσύνην</span><span class='greek-word'>ἐν</span></p><p class='inter-segond'><span class='french-word'>achevant</span><span class='french-word'>la_sainteté</span><span class='french-word'>dans</span></p><p class='inter-darby'><span class='french-word'>achevant</span><span class='french-word'>la_sainteté</span><span class='french-word'>dans</span></p></div><div class='interlinear-verse'><p><span class='greek-word'>φόβῳ</span><span class='greek-word'>Θεοῦ.</span></p><p class='inter-segond'><span class='french-word'>la_crainte</span><span class='french-word'>de_Dieu.</span></p><p class='inter-darby'><span class='french-word'>la_crainte</span><span class='french-word'>de_Dieu.</span></p></div>"
